ns%20Monday%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20Mike%20Waltz%2C%20and%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20among%20others%2C%20discussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-officials-weigh-in-security-leak-the-atlantic-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20plans%20on%20Signal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20group%20chat%20that%20mistakenly%20included%20the%20editor%20of%20The%20Atlantic%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d738f6d-6dde-4145-99db-b90c1696c775%5C%22%3E'I%20don't%20want%20secrets'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20the%20fallout%20from%20a%20mistake%20is%20worse%20when%20we%20try%20to%20outrun%20it.%20It's%20echoed%20in%20the%20Nixon-era%20precept%20that%20in%20government%20and%20beyond%2C%20the%20coverup%20is%20often%20worse%20than%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaficy%20said%20that%20in%20nearly%2029%20years%20running%20companies%2C%20he's%20never%20fired%20anyone%20over%20a%20mistake%20%E2%80%94%20though%20has%20dismissed%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20for%20what%20he%20saw%20as%20malfeasance%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20distinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20secrets.%20If%20there's%20an%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20if%20there%20is%20a%20mistake%20that%20has%20been%20made%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20surface%20it%20right%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Naficy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20can%20be%20especially%20intense%20for%20leaders%20who%20are%2C%20rather%20unrealistically%2C%20supposed%20to%20have%20all%20the%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAyanna%20Jackson%2C%20who%20founded%20and%20runs%20AEJ%20Consulting%2C%20an%20executive%20coaching%20and%20career-development%20firm%20in%20metro%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20bosses%20who%20are%20dominant%20or%20conscientious%20in%20their%20leadership%20styles%20might%20have%20a%20particularly%20hard%20time%20facing%20their%20blunders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20of%20those%20styles%20hate%20to%20be