e%20the%20error%20that%20was%20made%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jackson%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Hegseth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPentagon%20spokesperson%20Sean%20Parnell%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20the%20messages%20make%20clear%20that%20classified%20materials%20and%20war%20plans%20weren't%20shared%20and%20that%20Secretary%20Hegseth%20%26quot%3Bwas%20merely%20updating%20the%20group%20on%20a%20plan%20that%20was%20underway%20and%20had%20already%20been%20briefed%20through%20official%20channels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20didn't%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20actions%20of%20Waltz%20and%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20among%20others%2C%20in%20using%20Signal%20to%20discuss%20military%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec28d36a-1cc4-4ac9-a689-e5bc18c3df93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaying%20it%20all%20on%20the%20table%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20leaders%20see%20room%20for%20improvement%20in%20how%20top%20government%20officials%20are%20handling%20the%20Signal%20story.%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20John%20Thune%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmkraju%2Fstatus%2F1904910891113406683%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20CNN%20that%20those%20involved%20know%20they%20made%20a%20mistake%20and%20should%20act%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20own%20it%20and%20fix%20it%20so%20that%20never%20happens%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Hanslovan%20knows%20all%20too%20well%20about%20owning%20up%20to%20mistakes.%20He%20served%20in%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20and%20spent%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20working%20on%20security%20issues%20involving%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency.%20He's%20now%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Huntress%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Hanslovan%20said%2C%20an%20outsider%20gained%20access%20to%20Huntress's%20testing%20servers%20after%20the%20company%20left%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20intrusion.%20The%20weak%20spot%3A%20the%20password%20%26quot%3Babc123!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Huntress%20took%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20hack%20and%20went%20public%20with%20the%20issue%20even%20though%20customer%20data%20wasn't%20breached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanslovan%2C%20who%20wrote%20about%20the%20incident%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huntress.com%2Fblog%2Finvestigating-unauthorized-access-huntress-qa-environment-incident%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20post%2C%20said%20the%20transparency%20helped%20the%20company%20learn%20while%20also%20earning%20respect%20from%20clients%20for%20its%20candor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20forward%2C%20as%20a%20security%20company%2C%20built%20more%20credibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20trust%20in%20Huntress%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20the%20startup's%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20rose%20after%20the%20company%20disclosed%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanslovan%20said%20the%20company%20didn't%20fire%20the%20engineer%20responsible%20but%20instead%20used%20the%20situation%20to%20help%20the%20organization%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20engineer%20has%20actually%20been%20a%20really%20big%20part%20of%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20don't%20make%20those%20mistakes%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Hanslovan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20when%20you%20screw%20up%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20pause%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20can.%20Jackson%2C%20the%20executive%20coach%2C%20said%20she%20often%20encourages%20leaders%20to%20take%20a%20beat%20before%20rushing%20to%20social%20or%20in%20front%20of%20a%20microphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20your%20response%20is%20measured%2C%20appropriate%2C%20professional%2C%20and%20addresses%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20audience%20that%20you're%20talking%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsignal