EThe%20auto%20tariffs%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20on%20April%202%20and%20those%20on%20auto%20parts%20a%20month%20later%2C%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20factsheet%20said%20the%20new%20tariffs%20will%20apply%20to%20imported%20passenger%20vehicles%20(i.e.%2C%20sedans%2C%20SUVs%2C%20crossovers%2C%20minivans%2C%20and%20cargo%20vans)%20and%20light%20trucks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20parts%20like%20engines%2C%20transmissions%2C%20and%20powertrain%20and%20electrical%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20aside%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20exemption%20for%20Elon%20Musk's%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20do%20is%20(placing)%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20all%20cars%20that%20are%20not%20made%20in%20the%20United%20States...%20if%20they're%20made%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20it's%20absolutely%20no%20tariff%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20tariffs%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20growth%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20industry%20in%20America%20and%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20jobs%20and%20investment%2C%20claims%20that%20fuelled%20his%20re-election%20campaign%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20believe%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20temporary%20paralysis%2C%20affecting%20not%20just%20output%20and%20revenue%20for%20a%20cash-strapped%20government%20but%20also%20risk%20US%20jobs%20and%2C%20in%20addition%2C%20further%20strain%20ties%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Auto%20Tariffs%20Mean...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECar%20prices%20in%20the%20US%20-%20which%20imported%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%2016%20million%20sold%20last%20year%2C%20worth%20around%20%24240%20billion%20-%20will%20skyrocket%2C%20quickly%2C%20within%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20sharply%2C%20by%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tariff%20will%20also%20apply%20to%20cars%20'assembled%20in%20the%20US'%3B%20i.e.%2C%20vehicles%20put%20together%20in%20American%20factories%20with%20components%20manufactured%20elsewhere%20and%20then%20imported%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20to%20round%20it%20off%2C%20the%20tariffs%20could%20even%20affect%20cars%20'made%20in%20the%20US'%20because%2C%20as%20CNN%20pointed%20out%2C%20there%20really%20isn't%20an%20'all-American'%20car%20-%20which%20is%20what%20Trump%20wants%20and%20hopes%20his%20tariffs%20will%20force%20into%20being%20-%20since%20auto%20manufacturers%20in%20the%20US%20rely%20on%20parts%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20US%20auto%20industry%20-%20backed%20by%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20-%20has%20been%20able%20to%20treat%20the%20three%20countries%20as%20one%2C%20moving%20cars%20and%20auto%20parts%20freely%20between%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20manufacturers%20could%20set%20up%20factories%20in%20Mexico%2C%20for%20example%2C%20build%20engines%20and%20transmissions%20there%20and%20then%20ship%20them%20to%20a%20factory%20in%20the%20US%2C%20for%20no%20additional%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20though%2C%20could%20change%20after%20Trump%20begins%20taxing%20auto%20parts%20and%2C%20specifically%2C%20reviewing%20deals%20for%20free%20movement%20of%20these%20goods%2C%20which%20the%20BBC%20estimates%20is%20worth%20billions%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20don't%20forget%20the%2025%20per%20cent%20levy%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminium%2C%20both%20used%20in%20manufacturing%20cars%2C%20will%20also%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20experts%20believe%20manufacturing%20costs%20could%20jump%20by%20%243%2C500%20to%20%2412%2C000%20per%20car%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20fall%20in%20demand%20and%2C%20consequently%2C%20possible%20lay-offs%2C%20even%20in%20US%20factories%20to%20offset%20that%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Labour%20Department%2C%20over%20a%20million%20people%20work%20in%20building%20cars%20in%20that%20country%20and%20nearly%20a%20third%20work%20in%20auto%20assembly%20plants.%20It%20is%20these%20jobs%20-%20around%20half%20of%20which%20are%20not%20unionised%20-%20that%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20the%20first%20to%20go%2C%20as%20experts%20predict%2C%20once%20the%20tariffs%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Auto%20Tariffs%20Will%20Affect...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPretty%20much%20every%20foreign%20car%20manufacturer%20exporting%20cars%2C%20or%20auto%20parts%2C%20to%20the%20US%2C%20including%20big-hitters%20like%20Toyota%20(the%20world's%20largest)%20and%20Honda%2C%20and%20those%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetaliation%20isn't%20forthcoming%20just%20yet%2C%20with%20other%20countries%20perhaps%20waiting%20and%20watching%20to%20see%20if%20Trump%2C%20as%20he%20has%20in%20the%20past%2C%20rolls%20back%20his%20announcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%2C%20however%2C%20condemned%20the%20President's%20decision.%20European%20Commission%20President%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20underlined%20her%20belief%20that%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bare%20bad%20for%20businesses%2C%20worse%20for%20consumers%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20it%20will%20affect%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20integrated%20supply%20chains%26quot%3B%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Shigeru%20Ishiba%20has%20said%20his%20government%20is%20working%20on%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20measures%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20out%20his%20country%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20investments%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Canada's%20Mark%20Carney%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20country%20and%20the%20car%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20India%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20affect%20Indian%20manufacturers%3B%20shares%20of%20Tata%20Motors%2C%20for%20example%2C%20plummeted%20six%20per%20cent%20early%20Thursday%20morning.%20The%20company%20owns%20the%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%20brand%20for%20which%20the%20US%20is%20a%20key%20market.%20In%202024%20over%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20total%20sales%20were%20from%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuto%20component%20manufacturers%20like%20Samvardhana%20Motherson%20could%20also%20be%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20auto%20industry%20is%20not%20as%20exposed%20to%20the%20American%20market%20as%20those%20from%20other%20Asian%20countries%20-%20like%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20-%20or%20the%20EU%2C%20but%20there%20is%20still%20cause%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Indian%20companies%20exported%20over%20%242%20billion%20worth%20of%20auto%20parts%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20flip%20side%2C%20though%2C%20as%20far%20as%20India%20is%20concerned.%20Passenger%20car%20exports%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20insignificant%20at%20%248.9%20million%20last%20year%20and%20given%20Indian%20companies%20focus%20on%20controlling%20costs%2C%20its%20car%20prices%20could%20be%20appealing%20to%20the%20American%20market%20even%20with%20the%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743063420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjh0f2qmo_us-president-donald-trump_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-25-tariff-automotive-industry-impact-ndtv-explains-impact-on-india-8022347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20automobiles%20and%20auto%20parts%20imported%20into%20that%20country%20-%20and%20the%2025%20per%20cent%20levy%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20imports%20-%20mark%20a%20significant%20escalation%20in%20a%20global%20trade%20war%20brewing%20since%20he%20took%20oath%20in%20Jan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%