n-z-job-anxiety-stress-mental-health-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efelt%20more%20anxious%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethan%20they%20had%20the%20previous%20year.%20%26quot%3BAs%20life%20speeds%20up%2C%20maybe%20our%20vacations%20need%20to%20be%20slower%20to%20compensate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHotels%2C%20resorts%2C%20and%20retreats%20are%20stepping%20in%20to%20meet%20the%20need%20for%20a%20little%20TLC.%20In%202024%2C%20Miraval%20Resorts%20said%20it%20saw%20a%20nearly%2080%25%20increase%20in%20demand%20for%20stress%20management%20workshops%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20group%20arrivals%20have%20increased%20157%25%20since%202021.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20luxury%20consumer%20realizes%20that%20instead%20of%20acquiring%20things%2C%20acquiring%20experiences%20is%20much%20more%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dina%20Niekamp%2C%20the%20associate%20vice%20president%20of%20sales%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20brand%20for%20Miraval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EElla%20Dixon-Nuttall%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20yoga%20teacher%20from%20London%2C%20was%20tired%20of%20taking%20trips%20that%20revolved%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-beach-club-resort-worth-it-families-disney-world-review-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeach%20clubs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20drinking.%20So%20last%20June%2C%20she%20went%20on%20her%20first%20yoga%20retreat%20in%20Sicily%20with%20a%20friend.%20It%20cost%20%C2%A31%2C600%2C%20or%20just%20over%20%242%2C000%2C%20for%20the%20week%20and%20included%20accommodations%2C%20three%20meals%20a%20day%2C%20and%20yoga%20classes%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening.%20%26quot%3BYou%20got%20the%20benefit%20of%20an%20all-inclusive%20but%20then%20you%20also%20have%20the%20movement%20and%20wellness%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20home%20and%20feel%20filled%20up%20and%20energized%20by%20the%20experience%20rather%20than%20needing%20another%20holiday%20to%20get%20over%20the%20holiday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDixon-Nuttall%20enjoyed%20it%20so%20much%20that%20in%20February%20she%20went%20on%20her%20second%20retreat%2C%20this%20time%20with%20her%20mother.%20In%20March%2C%20she%20went%20on%20a%20third%20retreat%20in%20France.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20such%20a%20wonderful%20way%20to%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20now%20a%20retreat%20convert%20to%20the%20point%20where%20if%20I%20want%20to%20go%20somewhere%20I'll%20look%20if%20there's%20a%20retreat%20there.%26quot%3B%20She%20is%20looking%20to%20book%20another%20in%20India%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELili%20Paxton's%20mother%20is%20a%20similar%20convert.%20Growing%20up%2C%20Paxton%20recalls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpros-cons-skiing-italy-vs-colorado-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20ski%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20girls%20getaways%20to%20Palm%20Springs.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20Paxton%20and%20her%20mother%20were%20looking%20to%20book%20a%20more%20relaxing%20trip.%20They%20ended%20up%20planning%20a%20weeklong%20stay%20at%20Rancho%20La%20Puerta%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flost-100-pounds-wellness-resort-hilton-head-health-review-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewellness%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spa%20just%20over%20the%20San%20Diego%20border%20in%20Baja%20California%2C%20Mexico%2C%20after%20a%20family%20member%20recommended%20it.%20Weeklong%20rates%20for%20one%20person%20start%20at%20%245%2C650.%20Neither%20Paxton%20nor%20her%20mother%20had%20done%20anything%20like%20it%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20day%20hikes%20were%20offered%20at%205%3A30%20a.m.%20Classes%20were%20available%20each%20hour%20for%20everything%20from%20Pilates%20to%20pickleball.%20Paxton's%20mother%20tried%20Watsu%20%E2%80%94%20a%20type%20of%20water%20therapy%20that%20uses%20massage%2C%20stretching%2C%20and%20acupressure%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%26quot%3BShe%20said%20it%20was%20the%20most%20spiritual%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Paxton%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20said%20that%20she%20saw%20my%20dead%20father%20under%20the%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Paxton%20wasn't%20hiking%20or%20exercising%2C%20she%20was%20at%20the%20spa%20or%20relaxing%20by%20the%20pool.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20time%20I%20was%20just%20really%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20an%20escape%20from%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20left%20the%20trip%20transformed.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20is%20committed%20to%20going%20every%20year%20until%20she%20dies%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Paxton.%20%26quot%3BShe%20even%20talked%20to%20her%20financial%20planner%20and%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20need%20you%20to%20put%20this%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20the%20next%2020%20years.'%26quot%3B%20They%20spent%20another%20week%20at%20the%20retreat%20this%20past%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20people%20are%20happy%20to%20pay%20a%20premium%20for%20a%20chance%20to%20indulge%20in%20simple%20things%20like%20walking%20in%20nature%20or%20taking%20a%20deep%20breath%2C%20for%20others%2C%20wellness%20is%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-obsessed-longevity-luxury-hotels-iv-drips-mri-scans-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20high-tech%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%202008%2C%20the%20wellness%20resort%20Sha%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20holistic%20health%2C%20offering%20around%201%2C000%20different%20treatments%20in%20nearly%2040%20different%20medical%20and%20health%20specialties%20at%20its%20locations%20in%20Spain%20and%20Mexico.%20Stays%20at%20the%20resort%20start%20at%20550%20euros%20a%20night%2C%20or%20roughly%20%24600%2C%20while%20specialized%20four-day%20programs%20start%20at%202%2C500%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%242%2C700%2C%20with%20add-ons%20for%20treatments%20focused%20on%20sexual%20well-being%2C%20sleep%20recovery%2C%20stress%20management%2C%20gut%20health%2C%20quitting%20smoking%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BLeader's%20Performance%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20for%20example%2C%20starts%20with%20an%20advanced%20preventive%20diagnosis%20that%20tests%20body%20composition%2C%20cognitive%20abilities%2C%20and%20advanced%20glycation%20end-product%20accumulation%20%E2%80%94%20compounds%20that%20are%20linked%20with%20aging.%20Guests%20can%20also%20participate%20in%20clinical%20analyses%2C%20such%20as%20an%20oxidative%20stress%20test%20and%20a%20tailored%20meal%20plan%20with%20nutritional%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20type%20of%20treatment%20imaginable%20is%20available%20at%20Sha%3A%20stem%20cell%20treatment%2C%20advanced%20plasma%20renewal%2C%20hormone%20replacement%20therapy%2C%20sleep%20diagnosis.%20All%20guests%20receive%20an%20alkalizing%20diet%20tailored%20to%20their%20individual%20nutritional%20needs.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20go%20to%20see%20all%20these%20different%20experts%20in%20the%20city%2C%20first%2C%20it%20will%20take%20you%20months%20to%20see%20them%20all%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20no%20coordination%20between%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Alejandro%20Bataller%2C%20Sha's%20vice%20president%2C%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20probably%20the%20most%20comprehensive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sha%20appeals%20to%20a%20range%20of%20health-conscious%20consumers%2C%20Bataller%20has%20noticed%20an%20increase%20over%20the%20past%20two%20or%20three%20years%20in%20customers%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiohackers-build-house-to-help-them-live-longer-cost-features-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiohackers%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20These%20are%20people%20who%20already%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F74-year-old-exercise-routine-longevity-daily-strength-cardio-workouts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20doctor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nutritionist%2C%20and%20functional%20medicine%20doctor%20on%20speed%20dial%2C%20who%20take%2040-plus%20supplements%20a%20day%20and%20invest%20in%20the%20latest%20high-tech%20treatments.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20want%20a%20standard%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20come%20to%20Sha%20because%20they%20know%20that%20Sha%20is%20always%20cutting%20edge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBataller%20describes%20wellness%20as%20not%20just%20being%20healthy%2C%20but%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%2C%20ongoing%20pursuit%26quot%3B%20that%20focuses%20on%20improving%20yourself.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20someone%20with%20the%20best%20car%2C%20the%20best%20watch%2C%20the%20best%20suit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20he%20doesn't%20look%20healthy%2C%20that%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20luxury.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there's%20research%20backing%20up%20some%20of%20these%20treatments%2C%20Jessica%20DeFino%2C%20a%20beauty%20reporter%20and%20culture%20critic%2C%20questions%20how%20much%20is%20driven%20by%20health%20and%20how%20much%20is%20simply%20a%20medicalized%20beauty%20standard.%20%26quot%3BA%20better%20way%20to%20think%20about%20how%20we%20see%20looking%20healthy%20today%20is%20actually%20looking%20wealthy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20looking%20as%20if%20you've%20funneled%20thousands%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20into%20your%20face%20and%20body.%20That's%20not%20health%3B%20that's%20products%2C%20that's%20procedures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmen-corporate-america-expensive-beauty-routines-spending-thousands-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducts%20and%20procedures%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20the%20rage%20right%20now%20as%20people%20look%20for%20alternative%20approaches%20to%20well-being.%20%26quot%3BOur%20culture%20is%20largely%20unwell%2C%26quot%3B%20DeFino%20explains.%20Only%2036%25%20of%20Americans%20have%20at%20least%20%26quot%3Bquite%20a%20lot%26quot%3B%20of%20trust%20in%20the%20medical%20system%2C%20a%202024%20Gallup%20survey%20found%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Fdec%2F11%2Famericans-living-with-diseases-health-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20that%20Americans%20are%20sicker%20than%20people%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Only%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.medtronic.com%2F2024-04-17-Americans-favor-quality-over-quantity-in-pursuit-of-longevity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalf%20of%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20focus%20on%20eating%20healthy%20and%20exercising%2C%20despite%20diet%20and%20physical%20inactivity%20being%20leading%20contributors%20to%20chronic%20disease.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaratoga-water-exec-says-ashton-hall-morning-routine-is-amazing-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWellness%20gurus%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20stepped%20in%20to%20fill%20the%20gap%20left%20by%20a%20flagging%20healthcare%20system.%20Across%20social%20platforms%2C%20they%20document%20macros%20consumed%20and%20hours%20spent%20in%20REM%2C%20while%20touting%20the%20benefits%20of%20cryotherapy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-clinic-owner-reverse-biological-age-biohack-sleep-red-light-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered-light%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20hyperbaric%20oxygen%20therapy.%20%26quot%3BThe%20draw%20of%20wellness%20for%20the%20average%20person%20is%20it%20offers%20an%20individualized%20solution%20to%20a%20collective%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20DeFino%20says%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20intellectualize%20these%20arbitrary%2C%20oppressive%20beauty%20standards%20and%20make%20them%20seem%20like%20smart%20investments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20pursuit%20of%20chilling%20out%20isn't%20worth%20it.%20A%202023%20