ere%20are%20likely%20three%20broad%20categories%20of%20thinking%20going%20on%20here.%20There%20are%20those%20who%20don't%20really%20consider%20what%20they're%20doing%20to%20be%20stealing%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20oblivious%20to%20it.%20Like%20taking%20a%20pen%20from%20the%20breakroom%20at%20work%2C%20they%20figure%20it's%20baked%20in%20when%20they%20grab%20a%20snack%20as%20they%20browse%20the%20Whole%20Foods%20aisles.%20There%20are%20people%20who%20recognize%20it's%20cheating%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20think%20it's%20wrong%2C%20given%20Bezos'%20wealth%20and%20his%20business%20practices.%20In%20a%20context%20where%20Amazon%20has%20paid%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20settle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-paying-millions-to-workers-over-bag-check-lawsuit-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewage%20theft%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20figure%20lying%20about%20a%20lost%20package%20is%20a%20small%20way%20to%20try%20to%20even%20things%20out.%20And%20then%20there%20are%20those%20who%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20political%20desperation%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20powerless%20in%20the%20face%20of%20massive%20political%20and%20economic%20forces%2C%20and%20this%20is%20an%20outlet%20for%20some%20sort%20of%20action%2C%20even%20if%20futile.%20%26quot%3BThe%20target%20is%20misapplied%2C%20but%20the%20anger%20is%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20understandable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20try%20to%20neutralize%20potentially%20unsavory%20behavior%20by%20coming%20up%20with%20ways%20to%20justify%20their%20actions%2C%20Emmeline%20Taylor%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20criminology%20at%20City%20St.%20George's%2C%20University%20of%20London%2C%20said.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20tell%20themselves%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BBezos%20is%20bad%2C%20Amazon%20won't%20even%20notice%2C%20this%20seems%20like%20a%20victimless%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20themselves%20feel%20better%20and%20like%20they're%20in%20the%20right.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20sort%20of%20rehearsed%20this%20in%20their%20head%20so%20many%20times%20or%20even%20said%20it%20out%20loud%2C%20they%20start%20to%20believe%20it%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20allows%20them%20these%20sorts%20of%20moral%20gymnastics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20may%20see%20their%20actions%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20back%20at%20Bezos%2C%20the%20sheer%20size%20of%20the%20modern%20corporation%20creates%20a%20level%20of%20removal%20that%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20cares%20if%20someone%20pulls%20one%20over%20on%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20After%20all%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20they're%20pulling%20one%20over%20on%20us%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20take%20from%20a%20store%20or%20a%20workplace%2C%20it%20gets%20a%20little%20bit%20easier%20to%20distance%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Terrence%20Shulman%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Shulman%20Center%20for%20Compulsive%20Theft%2C%20Spending%2C%20and%20Hoarding%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20fact%20that%20theft%20and%20fraud%20are%2C%20you%20know%2C%20against%20the%20law%2C%20anti-Amazon%20avengers%20may%20not%20recognize%20the%20collateral%20damage%20they%20could%20be%20inadvertently%20causing.%20If%20you%20steal%20from%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20Bezos%20won't%20know%2C%20but%20the%20store%20manager%20who's%20fired%20over%20it%20will.%20(I%20did%20survey%20some%20Whole%20Foods%20workers%20about%20this%2C%20and%20several%20of%20them%20confirmed%20that%20(a)%20they%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20middle-class%20and%20even%20seemingly%20wealthy%20shoplifters%2C%20and%20(b)%20they%20may%20be%20a%20little%20bothered%20by%20some%20of%20it%20but%20are%20not%20in%20a%20tizzy.)%20Before%20you%20lie%20to%20Amazon%20that%20your%20package%20never%20arrived%20or%20return%20the%20wrong%20item%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20check%20who%20the%20actual%20seller%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Roman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20BattlBox%2C%20which%20sells%20outdoor%20gear%20and%20equipment%2C%20would%20rather%20just%20sell%20everything%20from%20his%20own%20website%2C%20but%20they've%20got%20to%20be%20on%20Amazon%20and%20other%20e-commerce%20platforms%20just%20because%20of%20the%20reach.%20He's%20currently%20dealing%20with%20a%20return%20fraud%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20bought%20a%20new%20spotlight%20from%20him%2C%20said%20they%20didn't%20like%20it%2C%20and%20shipped%20an%20older%20model%20back.%20BattlBox%20didn't%20even%20realize%20what%20had%20happened%20until%20they%20sent%20the%20returned%20item%20to%20another%20customer%20who%20flagged%20it.%20Roman%20has%20filed%20an%20appeal%20with%20Amazon%2C%20but%20there's%20%26quot%3Bno%20telling%26quot%3B%20whether%20the%20company%20will%20side%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20really%20blame%20people%20for%20doing%20this.%20By%20making%20returns%20so%20easy%20and%20taking%20%26quot%3Bthe%20customer%20is%20right%26quot%3B%20philosophy%20to%20the%20extreme%2C%20Amazon%20has%20fostered%20this%20behavior.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20average%20consumer%20even%20understands%20that%20it's%20not%20Amazon%20selling%20the%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Amazon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-copied-third-party-sellers-competitors-india-reuters-report-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregularly%20introduces%20an%20Amazon%20Basic%20version%20of%20a%20best-selling%20item%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20then%20gets%20prominent%20website%20placement%20near%20or%20above%20the%20original%20%E2%80%94%20in%20order%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-third-party-sellers-data-create-competing-private-label-products-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20in%20on%20the%20action%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Roman%20even%20understands%20the%20get-back-at-Bezos%20stuff%2C%20given%20how%20the%20ultrawea