edly-killed-by-revolving-door-8022037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lawsuit%20seeks%20damages%20for%20medical%20and%20funeral%20expenses%2C%20as%20well%20as%20compensation%20for%20pain%20and%20suffering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-hotel-sued-after-78-year-old-woman-was-allegedly-killed-by-revolving-door-8022037%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Three-Language%20Row%20And%20Some%20Hard%20Facts%20You%20Can't%20Wish%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIntensifying%20divisions%20between%20North%20and%20South%20in%20our%20country%20are%20getting%20increasing%20attention%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20about%20finances%E2%80%94the%20five%20Southern%20states%20contribute%20nearly%2029%25of%20the%20central%20government's%20tax%20revenue%20but%20only%20get%2015%25%20of%20its%20resources%E2%80%94or%20about%20political%20representation%20(the%20looming%20threat%20of%20a%20delimitation%20after%202026%20that%20would%20empower%20the%20more%20populous%20Hindi-belt%20states%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20South).%20But%20the%20issue%20that%20flared%20up%20last%20month%20and%20continues%20to%20roil%20the%20already%20troubled%20relationship%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20a%20somewhat%20unexpected%20one%3A%20that%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20A%20New%20Concept%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20three-language%20formula%20has%20been%20around%20for%20a%20while.%20It%20was%20originally%20introduced%20in%20the%201968%20National%20Policy%20on%20Education%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20promote%20multilingualism%20in%20the%20country%20by%20requiring%20students%20to%20learn%20three%20languages%3A%20their%20regional%20language%20(assumed%20to%20be%20their%20mother%20tongue)%2C%20Hindi%20(or%20another%20Indian%20language%20for%20Hindi-speaking%20states)%2C%20and%20English.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20suddenly%20became%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20again%20when%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20refused%20to%20release%20educational%20assistance%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20government%20under%20the%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20because%20of%20the%20state's%20failure%20to%20implement%20the%20three-language%20formula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Some%20States%20Are%20Upset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20has%20historically%20opposed%20the%20three-language%20formula%2C%20adhering%20instead%20to%20a%20two-language%20policy%20of%20Tamil%20and%20English.%20The%20state%20views%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Hindi%20as%20an%20imposition%20and%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20linguistic%20and%20cultural%20identity.%20The%20state%20has%20historically%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20resistance%20to%20%E2%80%9CHindi%20imperialism%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20passionate%20agitations%20and%20language%20riots%20having%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20past%2C%20even%20leading%20to%20self-immolations%20and%20deaths.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20state%20not%20to%20host%20any%20Jawaharlal%20Navodaya%20Vidyalayas%2C%20financed%20by%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20because%20those%20schools%20teach%20Hindi%20as%20a%20compulsory%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20also%20severely%20criticised%20the%20NEP%202020%20for%20linking%20central%20educational%20funds%20to%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula%2C%20denouncing%20such%20a%20move%20as%20coercive.%20He%20has%20accused%20the%20central%20government%20of%20using%20the%20NEP%20to%20push%20a%20political%20agenda%20and%20has%20vowed%20not%20to%20implement%20it%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Stalin%20has%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20the%20NEP%20could%20create%20hurdles%20for%20children%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20throw%20stones%20at%20a%20beehive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20declared%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20Union%20government's%20stand%20would%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20provocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShoddy%20Implementation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20defended%20the%20NEP%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20does%20not%20impose%20any%20language%20and%20aims%20to%20broaden%20educational%20opportunities.%20He%20has%20urged%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20rise%20above%20political%20differences%20and%20implement%20the%20policy%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20students.%20He%20points%20out%20that%20the%20NEP%202020%20in%20fact%20emphasises%20that%20states%20and%20students%20can%20choose%20the%20three%20languages%2C%20provided%20at%20least%20two%20are%20native%20to%20India.%20This%20flexibility%20aims%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20Hindi%20imposition%20in%20government%20schools.%20(Private%20schools%20increasingly%20offer%20foreign%20languages%20as%20the%20third%20option%2C%20driven%20by%20student%20and%20parent%20demand.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProponents%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula%20argue%20that%20it%20enhances%20linguistic%20skills%20and%20national%20integration%2C%20while%20critics%20highlight%20its%20uneven%20implementation%20and%20the%20socio-political%20tensions%20it%20creates.%20It%20is%20undeniable%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula%20in%20India%20has%20been%20inconsistent%20and%20influenced%20by%20regional%20politics%2C%20cultural%20preferences%2C%20and%20administrative%20challenges%2C%20including%20finding%20competent%20teachers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinguistic%20Diversity%2C%20And%20Policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20non-Hindi-speaking%20states%20typically%20offer%20their%20regional%20language%2C%20plus%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English%2C%20except%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%20Hindi-speaking%20states%2C%20however%2C%20the%20formula%20often%20includes%20Hindi%2C%20English%2C%20and%20rudimentary%20Sanskrit%E2%80%94an%20easy%20option%20that%20critics%20argue%20is%20a%20cop-out%20that%20doesn't%20fulfil%20the%20spirit%20of%20learning%20another%20modern%20Indian%20language.%20How%20many%20students%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20learning%20Tamil%2C%20point%20out%20critics%20in%20Chennai%20who%20resent%20being%20asked%20to%20learn%20Hindi.%20The%20answer%2C%20in%20government%20schools%3A%20none.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Indian%20states%20tend%20to%20stick%20to%20familiar%20northern%20languages%3A%20Haryana%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20implemented%20the%20three-language%20formula%20for%20Classes%20IX%20and%20X%2C%20making%20English%20and%20Hindi%20mandatory%2C%20with%20an%20optional%20third%20language%20from%20Sanskrit%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20or%20Urdu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-language%20formula%20has%20fostered%20multilingualism%20and%20national%20integration%20in%20many%20regions%20but%20remains%20a%20contentious%20issue%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20It%20highlights%20the%20complexities%20of%20balancing%20linguistic%20diversity%20with%20educational%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Coercive%20Federalism'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20government%20to%20withhold%20education%20funds%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20over%20its%20refusal%20to%20adopt%20the%20three-language%20formula%20is%20deeply%20implicated%20in%20the%20principles%20of%20federalism%2C%20state%20autonomy%2C%20and%20the%20role%20of%20conditional%20funding%20in%20governance.%20Inevitably%2C%20such%20a%20step%20looks%20like%20using%20the%20Centre's%20funding%20powers%20to%20blackmail%20the%20state%2C%20provoking%20the%20reaction%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20that%20self-respect%20demands%20that%20it%20not%20surrender%20to%20such%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20is%20a%20subject%20on%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20meaning%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20State%20governments%20have%20jurisdiction.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20argues%20that%20linking%20funds%20to%20compliance%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20infringes%20on%20its%20constitutional%20autonomy%20to%20set%20its%20own%20educational%20policies.%20What%20Pradhan%20is%20doing%2C%20they%20say%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bcoercive%20federalism%E2%80%9D%2C%20using%20the%20states'%20financial%20dependence%20on%20the%20Union%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20enforce%20central%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithholding%20funds%20under%20schemes%20like%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20affects%20critical%20areas%20such%20as%20teacher%20salaries%2C%20student%20welfare%20programmes%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development.%20This%20could%20disproportionately%20harm%20students%2C%20especially%20in%20government%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20Let%20Politics%20Get%20In%20The%20Way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government's%20case%20is%20not%20entirely%20weak%2C%20though.%20Proponents%20argue%20that%20linking%20funds%20to%20NEP%20compliance%20ensures%20uniformity%20in%20educational%20standards%20across%20states%20and%20promotes%20multilingualism.%20After%20all%2C%20conditional%20grants%20are%20a%20way%20for%20the%20Union%20to%20ensure%20that%20public%20funds%20are%20used%20for%20the%20intended%20purpose%20and%20align%20with%20national%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20implications%20of%20this%20debate%2C%20however%2C%20must%20not%20be%20lost%20sight%20of.%20The%20contestation%20over%20the%20three-language%20formula%20raises%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20balance%20between%20states%20and%20the%20Union%2C%20and%20between%20cooperative%20and%20coercive%20federalism.%20While%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20the%20right%20to%20set%20national%20policies%2C%20enforcing%20them%20through%20financial%20penalties%20can%20strain%20Centre-State%20relations%20and%20undermine%20the%20spirit%20of%20cooperative%20governance%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20himself%20touted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResolving%20the%20impasse%20over%20the%20three-language%20formula%20requires%20a%20balanced%20approach%20that%20respects%20both%20national%20objectives%20and%20regional%20sensitivities.%20Questions%20of%20regional%20identity%20are%20the%20reason%20that%20states%20assert%20their%20autonomy%20in%20educational%20policies.%20We%20can't%20wish%20this%20reality%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlexibility%20As%20A%20Virtue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20implementation%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula%20has%20varied%20widely%2C%20we%20could%20make%20flexibility%20a%20virtue%2C%20by%20allowing%20states%20to%20choose%20the%20third%20language%20based%20on%20their%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20preferences.%20For%20example%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20could%20include%20another%20Indian%20language%20or%20even%20a%20foreign%20language%20instead%20of%20Hindi.%20That%20would%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20Hindi%20imposition%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20NEP%202020's%20emphasis%20on%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20preferring%20incentives%20to%20penalties%2C%20and%20persuasion%20to%20coercion.%20Instead%20of%20withholding%20funds%2C%20the%20central%20government%20could%20offer%20additional%20incentives%20to%20states%20that%20adopt%20multilingual%20education%2C%20encouraging%20voluntary%20participation.%20It%20should%20also%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20policy%2C%20strengthen%20the%20teaching%20of%20regional%20languages%20across%20all%20states%2C%20including%20Hindi-speaking%20ones%2C%20to%20foster%20mutual%20respect%20and%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%2C%20instead%20of%20seeming%20to%20threaten%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20central%20government%20could%20adopt%20a%20conciliatory%20approach%2C%20launching%20a%20campaign%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20multilingualism%E2%80%94such%20as%20cognitive%20development%2C%20greater%20mobility%20and%20better%20career%20opportunities%E2%80%94to%20build%20public%20support.%20Another%20could%20be%20to%20implement%20pilot%20programmes%20in%20select%20schools%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20three-language%20formula%2C%20allowing%20states%20to%20assess%20its%20impact%20before%20wider%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENecessity%20And%20National%20Integration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20face%20one%20fact%3A%20People%20learn%20languages%20because%20they%20are%20useful%20to%20them%E2%80%94to%20survive%20in%20some%20environments%2C%20to%20get%20jobs%2C%20to%20communicate%20with%20customers%2C%20or%20just%20to%20enjoy%20popular%20entertainment%20(Bollywood%20has%20done%20more%20to%20promote%20Hindi%20in%20South%20India%20than%20the%20NEP%20has!).%20The%20three-language%20formula%20was%20an%20excellent%20idea%20in%20our%20multilingual%20country%2C%20but%20it%20will%20only%20really%20work%20when%20students%20believe%20that%20all%20three%20languages%20will%20be%20worth%20learning%20because%20they%20are%20useful%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20increased%20migration%20from%20northern%20to%20southern%20states%20for%20work%20and%20education%20has%20led%20to%20a%20greater%20need%20for%20Hindi-speaking%20migrants%20to%20learn%20southern%20languages%E2%80%94and%20often%20for%20their%20southern%20employers%20to%20master%20basic%20Hindi%20to%20communicate%20with%20them!%20Necessity%20is%20not%20just%20the%20mother%20of%20invention%2C%20but%20the%20spur%20for%20national%20integration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndians%20tend%20to%20assimilate%20wherever%20they%20go%E2%80%94whether%20it%20is%20Sikh%20dairy%20farmers%20speaking%20fluent%20Italian%20to%20work%20in%20that%20country%2C%20or%20Hindiwallahs%20picking%20up%20Tamil%20in%20order%20to%20survive%20in%20Kanyakumari.%20In%202019%2C%20Kerala's%20school%20board%20exams%20in%20Malayalam%20were%20topped%20by%20Dilshad%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Bhutto%20Sajid%2C%20an%20illiterate%20Bihari%20migrant%20labourer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20There%20Be%20Dialogue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20this%20episode%20makes%20clear%20is%20the%20need%20for%20collaborative%20federalism%20in%20our%20country.%20Whether%20on%20delimitation%20or%20the%20three-language%20formula%2C%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20establish%20a%20dialogue%20between%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20address%20concerns%20and%20find%20common%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20pity%20that%20the%20Inter-State%20Council%20has%20not%20served%20as%20a%20vehicle%20that%20assembles%20representatives%20from%20all%20states%20to%20help%20mediate%20and%20propose%20solutions%20to%20such%20disagreements.%20Such%20steps%20could%20help%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20national%20policy%20and%20regional%20autonomy%2C%20fostering%20a%20spirit%20of%20cooperation%20and%20mutual%20respect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20such%20a%20body%20could%20be%20created%20or%20revived%E2%80%94in%20time%20to%20promote%20dialogue%20on%20delimitation%20next%E2%80%94some%20larger%20good%20could%20yet%20come%20out%20of%20this%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20been%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Kerala%2C%20since%202009.%20He%20is%20a%20published%20author%20and%20a%20former%20diplomat.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743059820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fple516ao_language_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthree-language-row-and-some-hard-facts-you-cant-wish-away-8021134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Questions%20of%20regional%20identity%20are%20the%20reason%20that%20states%20assert%20th