036%20Summer%20Olympics%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20officially%20submitted%20a%20'Letter%20of%20Intent'%20to%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20in%20October%20last%20year%20to%20reiterate%20the%20country's's%20interest.%20According%20to%20a%20report%2C%20the%20Bhupendra%20Patel-led%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20initiated%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20for%20building%20the%20Olympic%20village%20and%20other%20facilities%20on%20a%20650-acre%20land%20in%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20quoting%20sources%2C%20the%20lands%20of%20three%20ashrams%20--%20Sant%20Shree%20Asaram%20Ashram%2C%20Bhartiya%20Seva%20Samaj%2C%20and%20Sadashiv%20Pragya%20Mandal%20--%20are%20set%20to%20be%20acquired%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20master%20plan%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20Olympic%20facilities%20for%20the%202036%20Games%20is%20being%20prepared%2C%20the%20land%20of%20three%20ashrams%2C%20including%20rape-convict%20Asaram's%20ashram%20in%20Motera%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20acquired%20for%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20Sports%20Enclave%2C%20Olympic%20Village%2C%20and%20other%20sports%20facilities%20coming%20up%20on%20approximately%20650%20acres%20of%20land%20near%20the%20present%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20at%20Motera%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TOI%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20added%20that%20the%20government%20has%20also%20initiated%20the%20process%20to%20provide%20alternative%20sites%20to%20these%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regards%20to%20the%20Sant%20Shree%20Asaram%20Ashram%2C%20Bhartiya%20Seva%20Samaj%2C%20and%20Sadashiv%20Pragya%20Mandal%2C%20the%20collector's%20office%20will%20complete%20pending%20proceedings%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%20The%20Land%20Parcel%20Finalisation%20Committee%20will%20decide%20on%20providing%20alternative%20land%20or%20compensation%20for%20constructions.%20Sadashiv%20Pragya%20Mandal%20has%20requested%20to%20retain%20structures%20at%20their%20current%20locations.%20The%20master%20plan%20may%20accommodate%20this%2C%20subject%20to%20cooperation%20in%20handing%20over%20other%20land%20parcels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20comes%20after%20another%20TOI%20report%20claimed%20that%20hosting%20the%20multi-sport%20event%20could%20cost%20India%20between%20Rs%2034%2C700%20crore%20to%20Rs%2064%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20estimated%20expenditure%20will%20be%20more%20than%20that%20of%20last%20year's%20Paris%20Olympics%20(Rs%2032%2C765%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20final%20blueprint%2C%20accessed%20by%20TOI%2C%20reveals%20estimated%20costs%20involved%20in%20bringing%20the%20sporting%20spectacle%20to%20the%20twin%20cities%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20four%20other%20cities%20--%20namely%20Bhopal%2C%20Goa%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Pune%20--%20placing%20the%20potential%20expenditure%20in%20the%20context%20of%20previous%20Olympic%20Games%20editions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2010%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20likes%20of%20Qatar%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20have%20expressed%20interest%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Olympics%2C%20though%20it%20is%20not%20known%20yet%20how%20many%20or%20which%20other%20nations%20have%20officially%20done%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decision%20on%20the%202036%20host%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20before%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743059580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fgavv38e4_india-olympics-_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Fasaram-bapu-ashram-land-to-be-used-for-indias-2036-olympics-infrastructure-big-claim-by-report-8021984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20development%20com