20Sunday%20(March%2030).%20Last%20year%2C%20Salman%20Khan%20didn't%20have%20an%20Eid%20release.%20He%20was%20last%20seen%20in%3Cem%3E%20Tiger%203%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0in%202023%2C%20which%20also%20released%20on%20a%20Sunday%2C%20coinciding%20with%20Diwali%20that%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20met%20the%20press%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20March%2026%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20release%20of%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20To%20ensure%20Salman%20Khan's%20security%20amid%20the%20constant%20threats%20from%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20no%20camera%20was%20allowed%20during%20the%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan's%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20tough%20competition%20from%20Mohanlal%20and%20Prithviraj%20Sukumaran's%3Cem%3E%20L2%3A%20Empuraan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethis%20week.%C2%A0The%20film%20released%20in%20theatres%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20NDTV%20asked%20Salman%20about%20the%20South%20vs%20Bollywood%20battle%2C%20Salman%20had%20an%20interesting%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%3Cem%3EL2%3A%20Empuraan%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20releasing%20just%20three%20days%20before%20your%20film.%20Prithviraj%20%5BSukumaran%5D%20wished%20you%20good%20luck.%20What%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%20about%20%3Cem%3EEmpuraan%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalman%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20love%20him%20as%20an%20actor.%20Prithviraj%20is%20directing%20it%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20excellent%20film.%20There's%20%3Cem%3EJaat%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20coming%20post%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20wish%20all%20of%20them%20do%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BWishing%20us%20good%20luck%5D%20That's%20really%20sweet%20of%20them.%20I've%20known%20Charan%20(Ram%20Charan)%20and%20Tarak%20(Jr%20NTR).%20They%20grew%20up%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20Most%20of%20them%20started%20doing%20films%20a%20year%20or%20two%20after%20I%20began%20my%20journey%20as%20an%20actor.%20I%20know%20Venky%20%5BDaggubati%20Venkatesh%5D%20really%20well.%20We've%20worked%20together%20and%20have%20been%20friends%20for%2030-35%20years%20now.%20I%20know%20Chiru%20Garu%20%5BChiranjeevi%5D%20because%20I%20did%20a%20Thumps%20Up%20commercial%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20South%20actors.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20was%20the%20first%20Hindi%20film%20actor%20from%20my%20generation%20to%20start%20working%20with%20South%20directors.%20I've%20worked%20with%20four-five%20South%20directors%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time.%C2%A0%20Even%20the%20heroines%20share%20this%20sense%20of%20brotherhood%20with%20me%3B%20it's%20really%20nice%20%3Cem%3E(laughs)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EHow%20are%20the%20South%20directors%20different%20from%20Hindi%20filmmakers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESalman%20Khan%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ETechnically%2C%20they're%20very%20advanced%20and%20emotionally%20they're%20very%20evolved.%20They%20don't%20pick%20up%20ideas%20and%20stories%20from%20elsewhere.%20They%20conceive%20their%20own%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20all%20the%20films%20that%20they%20make%20in%20the%20South%20are%20good.%20In%20Bollywood%2C%20you%20only%20remember%20those%20films%20that%20work%20well%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20%3Cem%3EWahaan%20bhi%20hafte%20mein%202-3%20picture%20picture%20banti%20hai%20but%20woh%20kuch%20khaas%20karti%20nahi%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2-3%20movies%20are%20released%20every%20week%20in%20the%20South%20too%2C%20but%20they%20all%20don't%20do%20too%20well).%C2%A0The%20mantra%20is%20the%20same%20everywhere.%20If%20you%20make%20good%20films%2C%20they'll%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESikandar%20%3C%2Fem%3Emarks%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Rashmika%20Mandanna's%20first%20collaboration.%20Apart%20from%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Rashmika%2C%20the%20project%20also%20features%20Kajal%20Aggarwal%2C%20Sathyaraj%20and%20Sharman%20Joshi%2