ns%20can't%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnimpressed%20by%20the%20explanation%20and%20the%20animated%20image%2C%20Mr%20Miyazaki%20said%20he%20had%20a%20friend%20with%20a%20disability%20who%20struggled%20with%20easy%20movements%20such%20as%20giving%20a%20high%20five%20because%20of%20stiff%20muscles.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20this%20animated%20image%20of%20unnatural%20movements%20reminded%20him%20of%20his%20friend's%20struggle%2C%20which%20is%20not%20entertaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Miyazaki%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffaroutmagazine.co.uk%2Fhayao-miyazaki-on-ai-utterly-disgusted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarOut%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20watch%20this%20stuff%20and%20find%20%5Bit%5D%20interesting.%20Whoever%20creates%20this%20stuff%20has%20no%20idea%20what%20pain%20is%20whatsoever.%20I%20am%20utterly%20disgusted.%20If%20you%20really%20want%20to%20make%20creepy%20stuff%2C%20you%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20it.%20I%20would%20never%20wish%20to%20incorporate%20this%20technology%20into%20my%20work%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20feel%20that%20this%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20life%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20presentation%2C%20the%20designer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20our%20experiment%20and%20we%20don't%20intend%20to%20do%20anything%20by%20showing%20it%20to%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToshio%20Suzuki%20also%20asked%20the%20team%20about%20their%20aim.%20One%20of%20them%20replied%20they%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20machine%20that%20could%20draw%20pictures%20like%20humans%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20latest%20model%2C%20GPT4o%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20an%20integrated%20image%20generator%20has%20taken%20social%20media%20by%20storm%2C%20with%20people%20creating%20and%20being%20in%20awe%20of%20never-seen-before%20Ghibli-inspired%20artwork.%