20the%20Tejas%20jets%20to%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20engine%20has%20been%20delivered%20to%20the%20HAL%20by%20the%20American%20company%20at%20its%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Lynn%20near%20Massachusetts.%20The%20engine%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20India%20by%20early%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGE%20Aerospace's%20F404%20family%20is%20known%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20aircraft%20engines%20and%20it%20powers%20thousands%20of%20combat%20jets%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Tuesday%2C%20we%20were%20excited%20to%20deliver%20the%20first%20of%2099%20F404-IN20%20engines%20to%20our%20valued%20customer%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL)%20for%20the%20Tejas%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20Mk%201A%20fighter%20jet%2C%26quot%3B%20GE%20Aerospace%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20important%20milestone%20in%20our%2040-year%20relationship%20with%20HAL%20and%20in%20our%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20a%20strong%20future%20for%20India's%20military%20by%20developing%20next-generation%20fighters%20while%20enhancing%20the%20country's%20defence%20manufacturing%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20F404-IN20%20engine%20is%20a%20tailored%20design%20for%20India's%20single-engine%20fighter%20programme%20with%20the%20highest%20thrust%20within%20the%20F404%20family%20and%20a%20higher-flow%20fan%2C%20unique%20single-crystal%20turbine%20blades%2C%20and%20numerous%20special%20components%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGE%20Aerospace%20and%20Tejas%20teams%20collaborated%20closely%20for%20several%20years%20to%20customise%20the%20engine%20for%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20F404%20demonstrated%20it%20was%20an%20excellent%20fit%20for%20the%20Tejas%20LCA.%20On%20its%20first%20test%20flight%20in%202008%2C%20the%20aircraft%20climbed%20to%20numerous%20mission%20altitudes%20and%20achieved%20Mach%201.1%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20engine%20maker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGE%20Aerospace%20said%20by%202016%2C%20it%20fulfilled%20its%20commitment%20to%20HAL%20and%20delivered%2065%20F404-IN20%20engines%20for%20the%20Tejas%20LCA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20no%20additional%20engine%20orders%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20the%20production%20line%20for%20F404-IN20%20was%20shut%20down.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20when%20HAL%20ordered%20an%20additional%2099%20engines%20in%202021%20for%20the%20Tejas%20Mk1A%20LCA%2C%20our%20team%20began%20the%20complex%20task%20of%20restarting%20the%20F404-IN20%20production%20line%2C%20which%20had%20been%20dormant%20for%20five%20years%2C%20and%20re-engaging%20the%20engine's%20global%20supply%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndigenously%20developed%20Tejas%20jets%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20mainstay%20of%20the%20IAF%20in%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20defence%20ministry%20accorded%20an%20initial%20approval%20to%20procure%20an%20additional%20batch%20of%2097%20Tejas%20jets%20for%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%20aircraft%20is%20a%20potent%20platform%20for%20air%20combat%20and%20offensive%20air%20support%20missions%20while%20reconnaissance%20and%20anti-ship%20operations%20are%20its%20secondary%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGE%20Aerospace%20said%20restarting%20a%20jet%20engine%20production%20line%20is%20a%20challenging%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRestarting%20the%20F404-IN20%20engine%20line%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20was%20even%20more%20challenging.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWith%20a%20high%20focus%20on%20safety%20and%20quality%2C%20and%20a%20remarkable%20commitment%20from%20our%20supply%20chain%20teams%20and%20our%20suppliers%20and%20partners%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20restart%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20proprietary%20lean%20operating%20model%2C%20flight