rl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAmused%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20As%20AAP's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20Flags%20Bank%20Conditions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20had%20a%20humorous%20response%20to%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20for%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20conditions%20of%20banks%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%2C%20in%20a%20friendly%20banter%2C%20said%20that%20Raghav%20Chadha's%20exposure%20to%20the%20western%20world%20would%20help%20people%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20amused%2C%20sir%2C%20if%20Member%20Raghav%20Chadha%20does%20not%20take%20offense%2C%20he%20observed%20the%20number%20of%20fans%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20how%20many%20were%20whitewashed%20and%20not%20painted.%20I%20am%20really%20so%2C%20so%20satisfied.%20There%20are%20members%20of%20Parliament%20who%20are%20otherwise%20very%20busy%20with%20many%20things%20internationally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20found%20time%20to%20visit%20rural%20banks%20and%20look%20at%20them%2C%20noticing%20there%20are%20no%20fans%20here%2C%20no%20doors%2C%20no%20chairs.%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%20please%20do%20more%20of%20this.%20It%20will%20help%20people%20within%20the%20country%20because%2C%20with%20your%20exposure%2C%20particularly%20to%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20you%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20here.%20Please%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20was%20seen%20smiling%20as%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20gave%20her%20response%20to%20his%20speech.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20severe%20crises%20affecting%20the%20country's%20banking%20system.%20During%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Banking%20Laws%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20he%20questioned%20the%20central%20government's%20intentions%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20bill%20does%20not%20meet%20public%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticized%20it%20as%20a%20bill%20focused%20only%20on%20procedural%20reforms%2C%20failing%20to%20address%20the%20real%20issues%20that%20citizens%20face%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20banks%20are%20not%20just%20financial%20institutions%20but%20the%20foundation%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20common%20people's%20savings%20to%20farmers'%20loans%2C%20from%20students'%20education%20to%20retirees'%20pensions%20-%20the%20banking%20system%20is%20deeply%20integrated%20into%20every%20citizen's%20life.%20However%2C%20growing%20banking%20fraud%2C%20loan%20recovery%20issues%2C%20and%20increasing%20pressure%20on%20employees%20have%20resulted%20in%20declining%20public%20trust%20in%20banks.%20Today%2C%20people%20are%20hesitant%20to%20trust%20banks%20with%20their%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20Chadha%20pointed%20out%20that%20home%20loan%20rates%20in%20the%20country%20have%20surged%20to%208.5%20percent%20-%209%20percent%2C%20while%20education%20loans%20range%20from%208.5%20percent%20to%2013%20percent.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20owning%20a%20home%20has%20become%20unaffordable%20for%20young%20individuals%2C%20and%20education%20is%20becoming%20excessively%20expensive%2C%20pushing%20students%20into%20debt%20before%20they%20even%20start%20earning.%20Additionally%2C%20MSME%20loan%20rates%20have%20reached%2011%20percent%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20set%20a%20maximum%20limit%20on%20education%20and%20home%20loan%20interest%20rates.%20First-time%20homebuyers%20should%20receive%20subsidized%20interest%20rates%20for%20affordable%20housing.%20He%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20RBI%20should%20promote%20small%20and%20digital%20banks%20to%20help%20lower%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20also%20voiced%20the%20concerns%20of%20senior%20citizens%2C%20highlighting%20the%20declining%20interest%20rates%20on%20savings%20and%20fixed%20deposits.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20FD%20rates%20stand%20at%206.5%20percent%20while%20inflation%20is%207%20percent%2C%20meaning%20savings%20are%20losing%20value%20over%20time.%20The%20Public%20Provident%20Fund%20(PPF)%20rate%20has%20dropped%20to%207.1%20percent%2C%20affecting%20long-term%20financial%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recommended%20that%20retired%20individuals%20and%20small%20depositors%20should%20receive%20a%20minimum%208%20percent%20interest%20rate%20to%20protect%20their%20savings%20from%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Banking%20Laws%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20warned%20that%20without%20a%20robust%20banking%20system%2C%20the%20entire%20framework%20of%20savings%20and%20credit%20would%20collapse.%20Millions%20of%20poor%20individuals%2C%20farmers%2C%20women%2C%20and%20youth--who%20rely%20on%20banks%20for%20their%20basic%20financial%20needs--would%20be%20left%20out%20of%20essential%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20deep%20concern%2C%20he%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20banks%20didn't%20exist%2C%20where%20would%20a%20farmer%2C%20who%20sacrifices%20meals%20and%20sells%20milk%20from%20his%20cattle%2C%20save%20for%20his%20children's%20education%3F%20How%20would%20a%20small%20employee%20gather%20emergency%20funds%20for%20tough%20times%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20banks%20provide%20the%20trust%20that%20hard-earned%20money%20will%20be%20available%20in%20times%20of%20need%2C%20helping%20farmers%20grow%20crops%2C%20families%20pay%20for%20medical%20treatment%2C%20and%20parents%20save%20for%20their%20daughters'%20weddings.%20However%2C%20this%20trust%20is%20now%20crumbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20Chadha%20also%20raised%20alarms%20over%20the%20rising%20threats%20in%20digital%20banking.%20He%20revealed%20that%2036%2C075%20banking%20fraud%20cases%20were%20reported%20in%20FY%202024%2C%20with%20digital%20payments%20and%20loan%20fraud%20being%20the%20most%20common.%20Cyber%20fraud%20caused%20losses%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202%2C054.6%20crore%20in%20FY%202024%2C%20while%20UPI%20fraud%20increased%20by%2085%20percent%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20questioned%20why%20public%20sector%20banks%20(PSBs)%20report%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20fraud%20cases%2C%20eroding%20people's%20confidence%20in%20the%20banking%20system.%20He%20recommended%20that%20banks%20should%20allocate%20at%20least%2010%20percent%20of%20their%20IT%20budgets%20to%20cybersecurity%20and%20implement%20mandatory%20biometric%20authentication%20for%20high-value%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%20issue%20of%20frauds%20related%20to%20KYC%20(Know%20Your%20Customer)%20updates%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20receive%20a%20call%2C%20and%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%2C%20their%20accounts%20are%20emptied.%26quot%3B%20Fraudsters%20trick%20people%20into%20sharing%20their%20bank%20details%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20updating%20KYC%2C%20leading%20to%20massive%20financial%20losses.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%2070%20percent%20of%20banking%20frauds%20occur%20after%20KYC%20updates%2C%20as%20this%20is%20when%20security%20monitoring%20is%20weakest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20questioned%20why%20banks'%20security%20measures%20are%20still%20inadequate%20and%20demanded%20stronger%20safeguards%20to%20protect%20customers'%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20expressed%20concern%20over%20Non-Banking%20Financial%20Companies%20(NBFCs)%2C%20increasing%20Non-Performing%20Assets%20(NPAs)%2C%20slow%20loan%20recovery%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20bank%20mergers.%20He%20warned%20that%20weak%20regulations%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20IL%26amp%3BFS%20crisis%2C%20could%20destabilize%20the%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20strengthen%20debt%20recovery%20tribunals%20and%20implement%20AI-based%20credit%20scoring%20to%20prevent%20bad%20loans.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20the%20RBI%20should%20cap%20ATM%20withdrawal%20charges%20and%20basic%20banking%20fees%20to%20protect%20customers%20from%20excessive%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20rural%20India%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20stated%20that%20despite%2077%20years%20of%20independence%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20still%20lack%20access%20to%20banking%20services.%20Digital%20banking%20is%20often%20discussed%2C%20but%20many%20villages%20lack%20proper%20internet%20facilities%20and%20financial%20literacy.%20Consequently%2C%20villagers%20struggle%20to%20open%20accounts%2C%20secure%20loans%2C%20or%20access%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20criticized%20the%20closure%20of%20over%203%2C000%20bank%20branches%20in%202022-23%2C%20most%20of%20which%20were%20in%20rural%20areas.%20This%20has%20forced%20villagers%20to%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20withdraw%20money%2C%20often%20paying%20Rs%2020-Rs%2023%20per%20ATM%20transaction%2C%20which%20is%20a%20heavy%20burden%20on%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20also%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20rising%20dependence%20on%20credit%20cards%2C%20which%20is%20pushing%20the%20middle%20class%20into%20financial%20distress.%20He%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20see%20credit%20cards%20as%20a%20convenience%2C%20but%20they%20unknowingly%20fall%20into%20a%20debt%20trap.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20sharp%20remark%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCredit%20cards%20provide%20relief%2C%20but%20high-interest%20rates%20crush%20the%20middle%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20promote%20financial%20literacy%20regarding%20credit%20card%20usage%20and%20ensure%20banks%20follow%20respo