ly%20for%20our%20meals.%E2%80%9D%20The%20couple%20realised%20that%20the%20existing%20models%20for%20freeze-drying%20food%20were%20not%20tailored%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333562%2Fassam-daily-wager-diganta-das-launches-paratha-startup-inspiring-entrepreneur-in-food-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eready-to-eat%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20wanted%20to%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20helps%20mothers%20send%20homemade%20meals%20to%20their%20children%20studying%20abroad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.29.38-2_11zon-1742741154-450x600.jpeg%20450w%2C%20https%3