ing.%20As%20Shalu%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20it%20as%20simple%20as%20possible%20for%20people%20to%20have%20a%20healthy%20meal%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20Whether%20you%20are%20at%20home%2C%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20or%20in%20a%20remote%20location%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20home-cooked%20meal%20ready%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%2C%20whose%20husband%20once%20struggled%20with%20finding%20vegetarian%20food%20while%20travelling%2C%20found%20the%20perfect%20solution.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20part%20about%20the%20brand%20is%20their%20tubs%2C%20as%20they%20are%20convenient%20and%20light%20enough%20to%20be%20carried%20across%20the%20globe.%20The%20food%20always%20tastes%20homemade%2C%20and%20each%20time%20we%20have%20purchased%20it%2C%20it%20has%20been%20consistently%20delicious.%20My%20husband%20now%20always%20carries%20a%20few%20tubs%20with%20him%2C%20and%20whenever%20he%20feels%20hungry%2C%20he%20simply%20adds%20hot%20water.%20Within%20just%20seven%20minutes%2C%20his%20meal%20is%20ready%2C%20and%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20him%20going%20without%20a%20proper%20meal%20when%20he%20is%20travelling.%20The%20peace%20of%20mind%20I%20have%20gained%20knowing%20that%20he%20is%20never%20left%20hungry%20is%20everything%20I%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20the%20heart%20of%20good%20food%20lies%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20those%20who%20cook%20with%20love.%20Homemakers%20bring%20that%20special%20touch%20to%20every%20meal%2C%20and%20with%20our%20preservative-free%20ready-to-eat%20meals%2C%20we%20are%20providing%20a%20connection%20to%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20Shalu.%20As%20the%20brand%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20the%20co-founders%20are%20planning%20to%20include%20a%20ready-to-eat%20snacks%20range%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Amit%20Murarka%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%2