ining%20the%20system%20to%20function%20seamlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%2C%20Gurneet%20Singh%2C%20has%20closely%20observed%20her%20journey%20of%20innovation%20and%20perseverance.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CTo%20date%2C%20I%20think%20Mannat%20must%20have%20competed%20in%2012%20to%2015%20competitions%2C%20and%20she%20takes%20the%20feedback%20seriously%20and%20ensures%20to%20make%20the%20necessary%20modifications%20to%20her%20prototype%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20highlighting%20her%20perseverance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20individual%20to%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20junior%20water%20prize%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20dedication%20and%20innovation%20led%20her%20to%20two%20prestigious%20competitions%3A%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20national%20chapter%20of%20the%20Stockholm%20Junior%20Water%20Prize%20and%20the%20International%20Stockholm%20Junior%20Water%20Prize%202024.%20At%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20she%20was%20among%20the%2010%20students%20selected%20from%20350%20applicants.%20Her%20ability%20to%20combine%20research%20with%20practical%20implementation%20impressed%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20presented%20the%20pitch%20effectively%2C%20showing%20both%20the%20research%20and%20implementation%20parts%2C%20which%20they%20liked%2C%20and%20I%20highlighted%20my%20project%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20people%20want%20to%20do%20and%20what%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mannat%20shares.%20Winning%20this%20competition%20earned%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20represent%20India%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mannat%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20her%20mecha